{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "c3d4e5f6-a7b8-9012-cdef-123456789012",
    "name": "Smart Licitaciones — Fase B (Catálogos + Config)",
    "description": "Pruebas de **Fase B**: módulos `catalogos` y `configuracion`.\n\n**Requisito previo (ubicaciones):** ejecutar una vez `npm run seed:ubicaciones` para cargar ~1123 municipios de Colombia y ~1892 distritos de Perú.\n\n**API:** ubicaciones geográficas = **solo lectura** (catálogo precargado en BD).\n\n**Flujo rápido:** carpeta **▶ RUN — Flujo automático** → Collection Runner → Run.\n\n**Variables auto:** `activationToken`, `preAuthToken`, `accessToken`, `operadorAccessToken`, `ubicacionId`, `departamentoCatalogo`, `paisCatalogoId`, `configDiasCrmValor`.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "event": [
    {
      "listen": "test",
      "script": {
        "type": "text/javascript",
        "exec": [
          "try {",
          "  const body = pm.response.json();",
          "  if (body.devActivationToken) pm.environment.set('activationToken', body.devActivationToken);",
          "  if (body.preAuthToken) pm.environment.set('preAuthToken', body.preAuthToken);",
          "  if (body.accessToken) {",
          "    const reqName = (pm.info.requestName || '').toLowerCase();",
          "    if (reqName.includes('operador')) pm.environment.set('operadorAccessToken', body.accessToken);",
          "    else pm.environment.set('accessToken', body.accessToken);",
          "  }",
          "  if (body.data?.[0]?.id && pm.request.url.path.join('/').includes('ubicaciones') && !pm.request.url.path.join('/').includes('departamentos')) {",
          "    pm.environment.set('ubicacionId', String(body.data[0].id));",
          "  }",
          "  if (body.ubicacion?.id) pm.environment.set('ubicacionId', String(body.ubicacion.id));",
          "  if (body.pais?.id) pm.environment.set('paisCatalogoId', String(body.pais.id));",
          "  if (body.data?.[0] && pm.request.url.path.join('/').includes('departamentos')) {",
          "    pm.environment.set('departamentoCatalogo', body.data[0]);",
          "  }",
          "  if (body.configuracion?.clave === 'dias_espera_respuesta_crm') {",
          "    pm.environment.set('configDiasCrmValor', body.configuracion.valor);",
          "  }",
          "} catch (e) {}"
        ]
      }
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "▶ RUN — Flujo automático (ejecutar en orden)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "1. Setup — correos únicos",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "prerequest",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const ts = Date.now();",
                  "pm.environment.set('adminCorreo', `admin-faseb-${ts}@local.test`);",
                  "pm.environment.set('operadorCorreo', `operador-faseb-${ts}@local.test`);",
                  "pm.environment.set('paisNuevoNombre', `Pais Test ${ts}`);"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            },
            { "listen": "test", "script": { "exec": ["pm.test('200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));"], "type": "text/javascript" } }
          ],
          "request": { "method": "GET", "url": "{{baseUrl}}/health" }
        },
        {
          "name": "2. POST Crear Admin",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "X-Admin-Dev-Key", "value": "{{adminDevKey}}" }
            ],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"nombre\": \"Admin Fase B\",\n  \"correo\": \"{{adminCorreo}}\",\n  \"rol\": \"Administrador\",\n  \"paisId\": {{paisId}}\n}" },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/users"
          },
          "event": [{ "listen": "test", "script": { "exec": ["pm.test('201', () => pm.response.to.have.status(201));"], "type": "text/javascript" } }]
        },
        {
          "name": "3. POST Activar Admin",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"token\": \"{{activationToken}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{adminPassword}}\"\n}" },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/activate"
          },
          "event": [{ "listen": "test", "script": { "exec": ["pm.test('200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));"], "type": "text/javascript" } }]
        },
        {
          "name": "4. POST Login Admin",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"correo\": \"{{adminCorreo}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{adminPassword}}\"\n}" },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/login"
          },
          "event": [{ "listen": "test", "script": { "exec": ["pm.test('200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));"], "type": "text/javascript" } }]
        },
        {
          "name": "5. POST Select Country Admin",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "X-Pre-Auth-Token", "value": "{{preAuthToken}}" }
            ],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"paisId\": {{paisId}}\n}" },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/select-country"
          },
          "event": [{ "listen": "test", "script": { "exec": ["pm.test('200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));"], "type": "text/javascript" } }]
        },
        {
          "name": "6. GET Listar países",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" }],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/catalogos/paises"
          },
          "event": [{ "listen": "test", "script": { "exec": ["pm.test('200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));", "pm.test('países', () => pm.expect(pm.response.json().data.length).to.be.at.least(1));"], "type": "text/javascript" } }]
        },
        {
          "name": "7. GET Departamentos (seed BD)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}" }],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/catalogos/ubicaciones/departamentos?paisId={{paisId}}"
          },
          "event": [{ "listen": "test", "script": { "exec": ["pm.test('200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));", "pm.test('seed cargado', () => pm.expect(pm.response.json().data.length).to.be.at.least(1));"], "type": "text/javascript" } }]
        },
        {
